2249
01:39:57.167 --> 01:39:58.768
Just leave the creative to me.

2250
01:39:58.792 --> 01:40:00.351
We just do that simple
black-and-white shot.

2251
01:40:00.375 --> 01:40:01.601
I don't want to do black-and-white.

2252
01:40:01.625 --> 01:40:03.143
- Why?
- Looks a little old-fashioned.

2253
01:40:03.167 --> 01:40:04.851
I think it'd be elegant
and chic. Old Hollywood.

2254
01:40:04.875 --> 01:40:05.917
So. here's the thing.

2255
01:40:06.833 --> 01:40:09.125
I've been trying to unload
Elias-Clarke for years.

2256
01:40:09.667 --> 01:40:10.976
Dad wouldn't let me.

2257
01:40:11.000 --> 01:40:12.476
Some sentimental hang-up.

2258
01:40:12.500 --> 01:40:13.518
But just now.

2259
01:40:13.542 --> 01:40:15.434
an offer just fell from the sky.

2260
01:40:15.458 --> 01:40:16.750
- So I took it.
- Uh...

2261
01:40:17.417 --> 01:40:19.768
- Sorry...
- [stammers] Sorry.

2262
01:40:19.792 --> 01:40:23.143
Are you saying that you sold
<i>Runway</i> to someone else?

2263
01:40:23.167 --> 01:40:26.893
I sold all of Elias-Clarke.

2264
01:40:26.917 --> 01:40:29.018
including <i>Runway.</i> to someone else.

2265
01:40:29.042 --> 01:40:29.934
No. you didn't.

2266
01:40:29.958 --> 01:40:30.958
Sorry. guys.

2267
01:40:32.292 --> 01:40:33.292
People.

2268
01:40:34.167 --> 01:40:36.934
- No. no. Wait. wait. wait...
- It could be a good thing.

2269
01:40:36.958 --> 01:40:38.893
- Wait. wait. wait. wait...
- No. no. Don't be upset.

2270
01:40:38.917 --> 01:40:40.059
Wait. wait. wait. wait.

2271
01:40:40.083 --> 01:40:41.101
I don't like it when you're upset.

2272
01:40:41.125 --> 01:40:42.893
How could you have let this happen to me?

2273
01:40:42.917 --> 01:40:45.292
Who did this to me? Who?

2274
01:41:06.292 --> 01:41:08.268
[Sasha] <i>I have complete confidence in you.</i>

2275
01:41:08.292 --> 01:41:09.226
- Hello.
- Hi.

2276
01:41:09.250 --> 01:41:12.351
<i>As the editor of</i> Runway <i>and
our global head of content.</i>

2277
01:41:12.375 --> 01:41:14.625
you'll have all the resources you need.

2278
01:41:15.250 --> 01:41:17.583
Show the world what you can do.

2279
01:41:18.250 --> 01:41:19.250
Oh. we will.

2280
01:41:24.500 --> 01:41:25.708
We will.

2281
01:41:27.750 --> 01:41:29.333
[chuckles]

2282
01:41:34.042 --> 01:41:35.851
[Andy] Do you think she'll
be able to stay out of things?

2283
01:41:35.875 --> 01:41:39.518
You heard her. Hands off. For now.

2284
01:41:39.542 --> 01:41:41.833
- [sighs]
- Mm-hmm.

2285
01:41:45.542 --> 01:41:47.208
You know. I should thank you.

2286
01:41:47.875 --> 01:41:50.958
You really woke me up. Somehow.

2287
