How did I know? Oh. Andy.

2291
01:42:04.333 --> 01:42:06.958
People run to tell you this kind of news.

2292
01:42:07.542 --> 01:42:08.542
They run.

2293
01:42:09.375 --> 01:42:11.583
No. you should write it.

2294
01:42:12.083 --> 01:42:14.292
