2295
01:42:14.792 --> 01:42:16.684
How impatient I am.

2296
01:42:16.708 --> 01:42:21.434
And... [sighs] ...demanding and imperious

2297
01:42:21.458 --> 01:42:23.976
and. you know...

2298
01:42:24.000 --> 01:42:27.351
how much of my
children's lives I've missed

2299
01:42:27.375 --> 01:42:30.625
and. yeah...

2300
