Maybe you're right.

2324
01:43:38.375 --> 01:43:40.750
Maybe I did it to keep my life. But...

2325
01:43:43.375 --> 01:43:45.833
Hmm. we can still do good work together.

2326
01:43:46.375 --> 01:43:48.000
Well. we have no choice.

2327
01:43:58.333 --> 01:43:59.518
- Pinocchio.
- [Lily] Mm-mmm.

2328
