- Oh. my God.
- [in Italian] <i>Altro Pinocchio.</i>

2330
01:44:02.542 --> 01:44:04.393
[Lily laughing]

2331
01:44:04.417 --> 01:44:06.351
[in Italian] <i>Pinocchio grande.</i> [laughs]

2332
01:44:06.375 --> 01:44:08.684
[in English] Andy. this is...
Thank you. This is very sweet.

2333
01:44:08.708 --> 01:44:10.851
but. you know.
she doesn't need any of this.

2334
