Yeah. I do. That's why we're sitting here.

2383
01:46:37.542 --> 01:46:39.559
No. I mean after you
left <i>Runway</i> the first time.

2384
01:46:39.583 --> 01:46:41.268
I called you.

2385
01:46:41.292 --> 01:46:42.559
- You called me?
- I called you.

2386
01:46:42.583 --> 01:46:43.667
You...

2387
